  <p>As a user of our Website, you may opt out of the use of the DoubleClick cookie for interest-based advertising by visiting the <a href="http://www.google.com/ads/preferences/" title="Ads Preference Manager" rel="nofollow">Ads Preference Manager</a>.</p>
